text:
@wholemars @StuartZuckerma1 ~4.5X increase in params should be ready for wide release later this year.

Super frugal use of memory bandwidth, caching exactly what is needed &amp; squeezing microseconds out of everything are needed to maintain the frame rate.

And the whole system needs to be retrained.

